Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.56,0:00:09.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你們兩個能不能不要一見面就吵起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.03,0:00:12.07,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是這傢伙先挑釁的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.24,0:00:14.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你說什麼  油炸豆腐團可是很美味的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.24,0:00:14.78,Kobayashi S2 - Comment,,0,0,0,,註：日語中的油炸豆腐團（がんもどき）和挑釁（がんをつける）諧音。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.03,0:00:20.04,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,畢竟你們從剛認識起就開始相互廝殺  也難怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.41,0:00:24.12,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不  我們沒有相互廝殺哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.62,0:00:27.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,確實  至少剛認識那時並沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.88,0:00:29.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那你們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.85,0:00:31.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是怎麼認識的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.23,0:02:08.02,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,聽說近期會發生內亂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.69,0:02:09.73,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.19,0:02:12.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,王位爭奪也到關鍵時刻了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.15,0:02:15.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,再這樣下去的話  鄰國會趁虛而入的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.65,0:02:19.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,人類還真是愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.70,0:02:21.91,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,張口就是爭鬥的話題
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.21,0:02:21.62,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,那個是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.66,0:02:23.37,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,是我先找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.74,0:02:25.04,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就不願意好好謳歌自己沒有價值的人生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.25,0:02:28.25,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,聖海的巫女大人駕到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.79,0:02:29.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,巫女大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:32.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她來到我們這座城了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.55,0:02:35.76,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這樣我們就得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.05,0:02:38.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,聖海的巫女  我知道她
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.79,0:02:43.47,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,據說她只要碰上人類的爭鬥就會將其解決
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.26,0:02:46.56,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,如果是為了水和食物而鬥爭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.68,0:02:49.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她就會創造出湖泊  帶來豐收
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.06,0:02:51.35,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,如果是勢力衝突
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.37,0:02:53.23,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她就會使用奇蹟之力使人喪失戰意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.94,0:02:56.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,神  或者是與之同等的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.24,0:02:58.03,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不管是哪一種
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.52,0:03:01.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,干涉人類社會都屬於違反規則
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:08.25,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那麼  她到底是何方神聖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:22.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:24.68,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,既不是神  亦非神之使者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.26,0:03:25.93,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,該不會是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:28.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,既然如此  她這是在鬧著玩的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:39.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你是在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.64,0:03:42.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,身為龍卻當什麼奇蹟的巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:44.41,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,笑死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.18,0:03:46.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我才想問
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.29,0:03:50.28,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,為何終焉帝的女兒會出現在人類的聚落
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.16,0:03:54.75,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我記得你好像叫托爾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.92,0:03:59.09,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我只是覺得同為人類不應該互相爭鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.83,0:04:02.05,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,無謂的流血十分愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.01,0:04:04.89,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,因為我有能夠阻止的力量所以我這麼做了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:07.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,在調和勢力的一堆懶鬼裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.02,0:04:09.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你倒算勤勉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.35,0:04:13.98,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,想必是獻祭給你不少人柱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.85,0:04:16.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我不需要人柱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:19.03,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你說什麼  為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.73,0:04:22.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,人哪裡好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:26.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這世上一定有許多更美味的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:30.54,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我相信人類會為我製作這些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:34.92,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,原來她就是魁札爾科亞特爾說的怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.33,0:04:36.50,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你就是艾爾瑪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:39.90,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不過  報酬就只是食物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.78,0:04:44.51,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,感覺你更適合混沌勢力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.97,0:04:47.80,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這麼說你也很怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:51.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,至今為止我所遇到的混沌之龍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:54.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,沒一個能順利交流
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:59.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我只是在消滅你之前先來看清你的真面目罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.94,0:05:01.69,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,看清我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.78,0:05:05.66,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那你要不要暫時和我一起行動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.91,0:05:06.41,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:11.66,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,和我一起看清這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:16.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那你們之後就一起行動了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.54,0:05:19.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:22.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我就陪著她自顧自地行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.14,0:05:25.43,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那時我肯定是腦子有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.93,0:05:28.51,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,也就是說你們在互相試探啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:33.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,兩人雖然價值觀不同  在互不侵犯的前提下行動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:36.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.98,0:05:40.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我只是對艾爾瑪感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.15,0:05:44.36,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,比起全族的目標  她更專注於自己想做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:47.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,因為當時的我也是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.78,0:05:49.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:51.12,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,後面的事就簡單了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.95,0:05:53.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,了解對方以後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.06,0:05:55.25,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,因為雙方性格不合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:57.04,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,幾十年後自然而然地發展成了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.58,0:05:58.58,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,互相廝殺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.50,0:06:02.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,一點都不自然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.55,0:06:10.18,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.09,0:06:12.85,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,為什麼要破壞宮殿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:15.89,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這裡原本會成為和平的象徵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.73,0:06:17.89,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,和平嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.60,0:06:21.56,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我只是對於你帶來的這種和平感到了一陣寒意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.86,0:06:22.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:28.45,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這座宮殿是為了將你奉為神明而建造的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.41,0:06:31.53,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,以你為根基的宗教將在此生根發芽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.08,0:06:36.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,然後形成階級制度  階級分化應運而生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.94,0:06:41.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不久之後就會向不信奉你的人開戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.24,0:06:43.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我會禁止這些事發生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.30,0:06:46.97,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我想說的不是這些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.05,0:06:51.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你想永遠和人類這樣繼續下去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:54.51,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不斷給予他們想要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.80,0:06:57.02,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,作為他們信奉的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.43,0:07:01.98,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我之前以為你是在按照自己的意志行動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:07.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你想就這樣被區區人類的社會所同化嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.93,0:07:11.12,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你已經背離初心了  艾爾瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:12.45,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我對你太失望了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.37,0:07:14.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我已經看不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:18.29,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我要殺了你  讓人類從夢境中醒來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.71,0:07:20.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真是大言不慚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.08,0:07:22.92,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,做得到的話就來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:29.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我其實也明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.72,0:07:31.68,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這種趨勢並不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.51,0:07:34.10,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是這不是沒辦法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:36.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,因為他們供奉的料理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:38.60,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好吃過頭了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.77,0:07:50.07,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這傢伙好強
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.76,0:08:15.35,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就這樣  我們最後分道揚鑣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:19.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,情節好像很壯闊  又好像很小家子氣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:23.81,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,結果我還是回到了調和勢力的據點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.44,0:08:25.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不再和人類扯上關係了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.58,0:08:29.07,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,也就是說你們是能吵起來的好朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.15,0:08:32.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林你有好好聽我們說話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:35.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,沒錯小林  我跟她就是沒有交集的平行線
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.95,0:08:36.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.69,0:08:39.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托爾在這邊就很聽話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:43.83,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,艾爾瑪也被工作壓得沒空去引領人類了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.72,0:08:47.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,在這邊的話應該就不用吵了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.09,0:08:53.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林  你不知道為什麼會變成這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:56.47,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,因為有好吃的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.92,0:08:58.89,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托爾和我都是吃貨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.76,0:09:01.24,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,果然跟你不可能合得來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.27,0:09:02.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.35,0:09:04.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不管說什麼都會扯上吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:08.52,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,要理解人類就應該品味人類的文化
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.57,0:09:11.19,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你只是嘴饞而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:14.49,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你不是也已經習慣人類的飲食了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.49,0:09:17.50,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,越了解對方的內心就會越親近
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.83,0:09:21.58,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不認同的地方就通過戰鬥磨合
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.96,0:09:26.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我也想要這樣的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.41,0:10:07.00,Kamisama S2 - Title,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(350,0)\pos(966.477,598.571)}與你一起  （要是心情好的話）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.08,0:10:35.53,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我要殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.28,0:10:39.07,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,整天遊手好閒的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.28,0:10:41.03,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,至少去工作下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.41,0:10:43.54,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我已經在考慮怎麼營生了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.95,0:10:44.68,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,再給我一百年
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.71,0:10:46.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不要用龍的時間跨度思考問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.29,0:10:51.58,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那我先幫托爾你幹活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.75,0:10:52.88,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:56.05,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,像你這種人怎麼可能做好女僕的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.30,0:10:57.55,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不要小看女僕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:11:00.51,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,明明你也天天被小林這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.97,0:11:02.51,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:04.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林也有在做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:05.56,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.97,0:11:08.18,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,也在賺你的生活費哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.62,0:11:10.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我知道了  我去工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.81,0:11:12.56,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那就去小林那
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.86,0:11:14.23,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我要消滅你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.40,0:11:16.15,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎麼了  好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.23,0:11:17.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,艾爾瑪也要消滅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:18.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,為什麼會扯上艾爾瑪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.28,0:11:23.91,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那就去找找會雇你的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.20,0:11:26.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,看看電腦上的或者招人告示
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.35,0:11:29.54,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不  我要自己看自己選
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.51,0:11:32.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那我們去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.38,0:11:35.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我還是第一次從這走過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.75,0:11:37.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,因為以前都是從屋頂上過的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.07,0:11:39.55,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好像貓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.29,0:11:42.43,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,還是放養你比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.88,0:11:46.43,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不過我還是要承認你付出許多努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.18,0:11:48.81,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,學會了使用認知妨礙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.39,0:11:52.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不知什麼時候起也學會了變成人手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.44,0:11:54.44,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,有好好努力了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.06,0:11:56.90,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我喜歡剛才那樣的托爾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.54,0:11:58.01,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.74,0:12:01.20,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不要突然說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:03.43,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但還是最喜歡小林
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.62,0:12:04.45,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.38,0:12:07.91,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好了  找到自己想做的工作了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:13.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,看見肉或者魚會情不自禁地吃完
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.83,0:12:15.50,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不愧是混沌勢力的同胞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.63,0:12:17.50,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,花也全都想踩壞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:19.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,破壞才是吾等宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.75,0:12:20.92,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,書就想全部燒掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:22.68,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,混沌勢力的榜樣
Comment: 0,0:12:23.26,0:12:25.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,雖然你都不可以去這些地方打工
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.26,0:12:25.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,雖然這些事情全都不能在這裡做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.78,0:12:27.01,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.47,0:12:29.97,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這種類似本能的衝動有時挺討人厭的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:33.10,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但我們正是因為要克制本能才來到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.65,0:12:34.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托爾你做到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.31,0:12:36.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.77,0:12:39.98,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是好像找不到可以打工的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.24,0:12:41.24,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,來玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.37,0:12:43.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,可以啊  一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.16,0:12:45.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,一起去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:46.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.64,0:12:47.41,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,買東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.62,0:12:48.45,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.62,0:12:49.58,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.37,0:12:51.75,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.75,0:12:55.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小康納  才川同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.17,0:12:56.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你們來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.15,0:12:58.80,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托爾大人和伊露露
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:01.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:03.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你們才是為什麼在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.42,0:13:05.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我們是這裡的老顧客
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.30,0:13:09.51,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,原來姐姐們是康納的熟人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.82,0:13:10.85,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我是托爾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.06,0:13:12.02,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這位是伊露露
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.77,0:13:14.98,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我們正在尋找打工的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:20.53,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,選哪個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.63,0:13:21.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,味道都一樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.78,0:13:23.19,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.53,0:13:25.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這個好像很適合小康納
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.65,0:13:26.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,才川同學也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.54,0:13:32.20,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,成對的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.60,0:13:35.83,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,第一次見的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:38.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是女僕的妹妹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.04,0:13:41.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這裡原來是會田婆婆開的店啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.88,0:13:43.88,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,伊露露  這位是會田婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.49,0:13:47.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我們在居委會的聚會上經常見面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.04,0:13:50.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,您的腳怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:53.18,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,慢跑的時候傷到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.43,0:13:54.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,年紀也差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.64,0:13:56.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,都想著要不把店給關了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:13:57.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.65,0:14:00.51,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:01.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,再想辦法撐一會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.19,0:14:05.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好多小孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:07.41,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,因為是小賣部
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.21,0:14:09.24,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,幾十年來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.41,0:14:11.66,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,一批又一批的孩子都會來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.41,0:14:13.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我可以在這裡工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.37,0:14:16.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你多少歲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:18.58,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,和我一樣大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.88,0:14:20.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,和女僕一樣大嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.88,0:14:23.09,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.67,0:14:26.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,本想著交給孫子來幹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.84,0:14:31.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,與其強求他接手  還是交給有幹勁的人更好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:33.01,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我也拜託您了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.39,0:14:47.15,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.57,0:14:50.07,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,在小賣部打工啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.01,0:14:52.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,朧家小賣部
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.92,0:14:54.27,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.70,0:14:56.75,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是商店街邊上那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.33,0:15:01.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她能被僱傭  都是看在我幫你說話的份上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.67,0:15:05.55,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,蠱惑人心  果然你這傢伙很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.65,0:15:06.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,再多夸點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:08.51,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這是在誇你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:14.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我能幹好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.72,0:15:17.25,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你是在不安嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:20.19,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是憑自己興趣選的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.72,0:15:32.49,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我是循序漸進幹一段時間才開始有成就感的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.41,0:15:34.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,以這種方式進入職場
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.11,0:15:36.20,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我覺得挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.79,0:15:39.83,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.46,0:15:42.88,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托爾也對女僕感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.96,0:15:44.54,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,非常有成就感
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.04,0:15:46.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,所以快摸摸我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.01,0:15:50.04,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,伊露露  要好好聽人家的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.27,0:15:52.47,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,記住正確的業務內容
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.14,0:15:55.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,可不要變得像這個女僕一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.60,0:15:58.85,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小…小林
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.68,0:16:35.85,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎麼了  阿竹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.30,0:16:38.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我家奶奶傷到腳了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.18,0:16:40.27,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,所以叫你幫忙看店嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.39,0:16:44.81,Kobayashi S2 - Name,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\pos(966.4,887.143)\3c&H1C18D0&}會田竹人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:42.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不用  好像是雇了人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.78,0:16:44.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,讓我去稍微指導一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.31,0:16:48.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那個古怪婆婆居然會招外人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:51.69,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,然後今天也叫我把衣服帶過去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.48,0:16:53.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你看這件衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.41,0:16:56.12,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這可是成年男性的尺寸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.81,0:16:59.04,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,也就是說雇的是個男人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.34,0:17:00.87,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,也不知道是在哪裡認識的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.23,0:17:02.91,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,要是個怪人我就把他攆出去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.50,0:17:05.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,夠威猛啊  竹人同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.29,0:17:06.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,一邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.31,0:17:09.75,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真是的  究竟是個什麼樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.05,0:17:11.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.51,0:17:14.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,大人的尺寸  好勁爆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.95,0:17:18.35,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,會田奶奶的孫子？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.97,0:17:20.01,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我是會田竹人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.39,0:17:21.52,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我是伊露露
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.81,0:17:22.48,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,16歲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.68,0:17:23.85,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,對外宣稱是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.19,0:17:25.10,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,同齡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.52,0:17:27.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,名字挺像是外國人的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.17,0:17:29.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,在哪裡認識奶奶的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.40,0:17:31.23,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就在這裡遇見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:33.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,然後我問能不能讓我在這打工  就錄用了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:35.11,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,決定得也太隨便了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.36,0:17:37.20,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.69,0:17:40.67,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,突然想到小賣部打工應該是有什麼緣由的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.03,0:17:42.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,所以你來幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.21,0:17:44.87,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,把衣服給你送來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.54,0:17:46.67,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,圍裙和白襯衫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.00,0:17:47.92,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,著裝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.46,0:17:49.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.92,0:17:52.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,痴女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.55,0:17:53.55,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你是痴女嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.67,0:17:55.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,對啊  要害羞來著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.38,0:17:56.22,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,確實是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.43,0:17:57.09,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,色狼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.97,0:17:59.51,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,別邊害羞邊脫衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.26,0:18:01.56,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,給我到裡面換
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.02,0:18:03.27,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,要這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.43,0:18:05.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.88,0:18:07.60,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,從有那種風俗文化的國家來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.81,0:18:08.73,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好想去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.06,0:18:10.27,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我說竹人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.60,0:18:11.48,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,叫阿竹就行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.21,0:18:12.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.41,0:18:15.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,衣服的扣子扣不上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.32,0:18:18.03,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這樣就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.49,0:18:19.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:21.91,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你好色呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:23.33,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.79,0:18:24.54,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,一直盯著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.58,0:18:26.50,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,沒…我沒看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.04,0:18:29.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.13,0:18:30.92,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,有什麼不懂的事情就來問我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.05,0:18:35.97,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,可疑的方向不大對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:40.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真虧奶奶會想僱傭這個謎一般的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.64,0:18:42.97,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,和心懷不軌的人比起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.97,0:18:44.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這種人完全搞不懂反而更可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.48,0:18:47.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這傢伙這樣能幹好活嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.42,0:18:48.52,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我要這個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:49.52,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,多謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.73,0:18:50.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,幫我拿下那個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.71,0:18:52.36,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.63,0:18:53.23,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,對
Comment: 0,0:18:53.32,0:18:55.69,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/水氣球
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.99,0:18:55.69,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這個可以一個個賣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.79,0:18:57.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,可以
Comment: 0,0:18:57.45,0:19:01.20,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/抽獎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.28,0:19:01.28,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這傢伙在認真幹活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.49,0:19:00.66,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.24,0:19:04.02,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不  比我還認真
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.66,0:19:06.83,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這就是奶奶把工作交給她的理由嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.66,0:19:08.19,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,好大  為什麼胸能這麼大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.79,0:19:10.83,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,純真無知的小學生的性騷擾高速球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:11.88,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,如何迴避呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.89,0:19:13.35,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這裡是火焰袋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.68,0:19:15.51,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,因為要存放火焰所以很大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.66,0:19:16.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.00,0:19:18.93,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,轉移話題的方式咋這麼奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.28,0:19:20.43,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,果然很重嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.01,0:19:21.97,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,肩膀會酸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.85,0:19:25.01,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,要不你掂一掂試試
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.27,0:19:26.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,等等  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.85,0:19:28.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你別做些奇怪的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.53,0:19:35.98,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你沒事吧  阿竹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.44,0:19:38.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.87,0:19:41.59,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,對哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.12,0:19:42.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你個色狼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.12,0:19:45.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,為什麼反應慢了一拍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.83,0:19:47.87,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.50,0:19:49.50,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.87,0:19:51.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,下次再見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.59,0:19:59.76,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,其實我喜歡小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.59,0:20:02.09,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,喜歡和小孩玩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.18,0:20:06.22,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是工作就不能和小孩玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.14,0:20:10.10,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,所以我想在有孩子們玩樂的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.86,0:20:17.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,到關門的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.26,0:20:20.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,稍微玩會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.90,0:20:23.03,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我教你怎麼玩陀螺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.82,0:20:25.49,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那個嗎  快教我  快教我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.78,0:20:26.49,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我去拿來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.22,0:20:28.49,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這傢伙挺不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.20,0:20:30.83,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這樣一來奶奶也放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.92,0:20:34.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,阿竹  我中意你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.71,0:20:36.29,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,什麼  這是我該說的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.29,0:20:37.48,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,僅次於小林
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.42,0:20:39.01,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.80,0:20:40.63,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.56,0:20:42.63,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:44.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.48,0:20:52.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.92,0:20:55.90,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,人類會向星星許願
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.27,0:21:02.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,為了自己或家人的幸福  豐收或和平
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.94,0:21:04.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,都會向星星許願
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.82,0:21:07.66,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,只要可以實現願望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.91,0:21:09.58,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,向誰許願都行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.72,0:21:12.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,愈發深感這類生物真是下等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.77,0:21:15.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,要是你的話會許什麼願
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.85,0:21:17.63,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,要是願望能實現的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.01,0:21:23.01,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.43,0:21:27.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,要是我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.51,0:21:29.68,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,反正肯定是想吃好多好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.01,0:21:30.47,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.06,0:21:33.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你不是很懂我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.99,0:21:37.02,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是  不止於此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.48,0:21:38.09,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,還有什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.78,0:21:41.85,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我會祈願你也能享受到同樣份的美食
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.95,0:21:47.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,隨便你
Comment: 0,0:21:50.03,0:21:50.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,---ED---
