Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.99,0:22:28.62,Kabayashi S2 - EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}打架啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.66,0:22:31.37,Kabayashi S2 - EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}比起這小小世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.95,0:22:35.21,Kabayashi S2 - EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}各有不同的心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.33,0:22:37.42,Kabayashi S2 - EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}才是能夠展翅高飛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.67,0:22:43.92,Kabayashi S2 - EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}廣闊而溫暖的歸宿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.55,0:22:49.22,Kabayashi S2 - EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}只要大家都在一起比什麼都好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.26,0:22:52.31,Kabayashi S2 - EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Made！Made！Made！付出全部心血！
