Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.69,0:22:59.15,Kabayashi S2 - EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\3c&H4789EB&\4c&H4789EB&}讓我們！盡情地！謳歌吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.52,0:23:02.73,Kabayashi S2 - EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}自出生起就一直如此
